<!-- ACTIVITY PROGRAMMING INFO -->
<section class="section section--cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-split">
      <div class="intro-split__media reveal">
        <img src="{{ images.residentsLaughing }}" alt="Residents enjoying activities and social time together" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <div class="intro-split__body reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Full-Time Activity Director</span>
        <h2>Every day planned around you.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Azalea Estates employs a full-time Activity Director whose sole focus is finding out what residents enjoy most and building a daily calendar of events around those preferences.</p>
        <p>This isn&rsquo;t a bingo-and-puzzles approach to programming. Our Activity Director manages a rich schedule of social interaction, cultural enrichment, physical engagement, faith services, and community partnership events that keep residents looking forward to each new day.</p>
        <p>Being in Fayette County means being close to everything. We take full advantage of that — coordinating day trips and evening outings to Fox Theatre productions, concerts, the Atlanta Botanical Gardens, Braves games, and cultural events across greater Atlanta. Closer to home, residents enjoy local favorites in Fayetteville and Peachtree City throughout the year.</p>
        <p>When there&rsquo;s no reason to leave, our team brings the celebration to campus. Common areas become a haunted mansion for Halloween, a ballroom for the Valentine&rsquo;s dance, and a venue for educational seminars with guest speakers covering everything from local news to national and world affairs. We also invite local churches, school children, and civic organizations in regularly, keeping Azalea Estates woven into the fabric of the broader community.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

