      </div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal">
        <div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('book', 22) }}</div>
        <div><h4>Arts, Crafts &amp; Learning</h4><p>Creative workshops, book clubs, and educational seminars with guest speakers on local, national, and world topics that keep minds active and engaged.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="amenity-chip reveal">
        <div class="amenity-chip__icon">{{ icon('heart', 22) }}</div>
